    [2022-08-01 EG]
    See SourceForge bugs #61 and #68.  Note that #61 is different as Fred is a directory being
    added, not a file.  zipsleuth has issues with the #61 file.
    Priority:  1
    REFERENCES:
    Status:  PENDING         Target Release:  3.1e    Estimated Work:  SMALL
    
Mar 30 email 509P

